        <num>CCP 3508</num>
        <heading>3508.  Amount of security for release of attached or sequestered property</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 3508.  Amount of security for release of attached or sequestered property
The security for the release of property seized under a writ of attachment or of sequestration shall exceed by one-fourth the value of the property as determined by the court, or shall exceed by one-fourth the amount of the claim, whichever is the lesser.</p>
        </content>
        <authorialNote marker="source">
          <p>Source: https://www.legis.la.gov/legis/Law.aspx?d=111784</p>
        </authorialNote>
